      • parse

        public static java.util.BitSet parse(java.lang.String s)
        Parses a string of '0' and '1' characters interpreted in big-endian format and transforms it into a BitSet.

        Whitespaces are ignored.

        Parameters:
        s - the input string
        Returns:
        A BitSet whose bits at indices are set to true, when the reversed input string has a '1' character at the same index.
